Al-Sadr Calls for Resistance Eight Years After Fall of Baghdad

-- B y   K a d h i m   A j r a s h
-- 
2011-04-09T08:53:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-09/al-sadr-calls-for-resistance-eight-years-after-fall-of-baghdad.html
Iraqi Shiite Muslim cleric Moqtada al-Sadr marked the eighth anniversary of the fall of  Baghdad 
today by calling on his followers to step up resistance if U.S.
troops don’t leave.  Speaking before tens of thousands of supporters, al-Sadr
called for an increase in military and popular resistance
against the “invaders.”  To contact the reporters on this story:
Kadhim Ajrash in Baghdad at 
 kadhimajrash@yahoo.com ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net . 